                  <handDesc>
                     <!--ACHTUNG! first HandNote comes from writing system in Ethiospare. the others are one for each CHANGE OF HAND-->
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                        <seg type="script">Hand a: rather fine. Hand b: mediocre, uneven.</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black; red.</seg>
                        <date>19th century (?).</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>
                              <abbr>ወክ፡</abbr> for <expan>ወክፍል፡ </expan> (<locus target="#11rb">11rb</locus>).</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Three pairs of lines on the incipit page of Text I
                           alternating with black lines; title or incipit of the subsections of Text
                           I; name of St Mary on fol. 9ra; elements of the punctuation signs and of
                           Ethiopic numerals; tables on fols. 2r-7v, 18rv; some Ethiopic numerals in
                           the tables on fols. 2r-7v.</seg>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h2" script="Ethiopic">Hand a: fols. 1-14v, 17r.
                        <!--The names of this hands need to be replaced by appropriate refs.--></handNote>
                     <handNote xml:id="h3" script="Ethiopic"> Hand b: <locus from="15r" to="16v">15r-16v</locus>.<!--The names of this hands need to be replaced by appropriate refs.--></handNote>
                  </handDesc>
                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1"> <locus target="#1va">f. 1va</locus>
                           <desc>-b </desc>
                           <locus target="#19">19</locus>: Note on computation of the feasts. <q xml:lang="gez"> <locus target="#1va">1va-</locus>b <locus target="#19">19</locus>: አልቦ፡ አበቅቴ፡ ወአልቦ፡ መጥቅዕ፡ በሆነ፡ ጊዜ፡ ፩ መጥቅዕ፡ ማድረግ፡ አይገባም፡
                              ዘይገብር፡ ፩ደ፡ መጥቅዐ፡ ውጉዝ፡ ለይኩን፡ ብሎ፡ ሊቁ፡ አውግዞታል። …</q>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The note is written in Amharic and Gǝʿǝz. It contains instructions
                              for calculating the mobile feasts of the year. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2"> <locus target="#1vb">f. 1vb</locus>
                           <desc> </desc>
                           <locus from="12" to="20">12-20</locus>: Chronological note. <q xml:lang="gez"> <locus target="#1vb">1vb</locus>
                              <locus from="12" to="20">12-20</locus>: እምስብካት፡ ሐዋርያት፡ እስከ፡ መንግሥተ፡
                              ድዮቅልጥያኖስ፡ ፪፻፸ወ፯ዓመት፡ እመንግሥተ፡ ድዮቅልጥያኖስ፡ ፶፱ዓመት፡ ኮነ፡ ጉባዒ፡ ኒቅያ፡ በመዋዕለ፡
                              ቈስጠንጢኖስ፡ …</q>
                           <note> The note indicates the number of years between the preaching of
                              the Apostles and the reign of Diocletian (277 years), between the
                              reign of Diocletian and the Council of Nicaea (59 years), between the
                              reign of Diocletian and the Council of Constantinople (117 years).
                           </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3"> <locus target="#1vb">f. 1vb</locus>
                           <desc> </desc>
                           <locus from="21" to="26">21-26</locus>: Chronological note. <q xml:lang="gez"> <locus target="#1vb">1vb</locus>
                              <locus from="21" to="26">21-26</locus>: በዮሐንስ፡ ተፀነሰ፡ በማቴዎስ፡ ተወለደ፡
                              በሉቃስ፡ ተጠመቀ፡ በማርቆስ፡ ተሰቀለ፡ …</q>
                           <note> The note is crudely written. It indicates the years in which Jesus
                              Christ was conceived, born, baptized and crucified. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4"> <locus target="#8ra">f. 8ra</locus>
                           <desc>: Ownership note. </desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"> <locus target="#8ra">8ra</locus>: ዘመጽሐፍ፡ ዘአበሐይለ፡
                              ሚካኤል።</q> The note is written in red ink and is encircled in a frame
                           in black ink. It states that ʾabbā<note> Ḫāyla Mikāʾel is the owner of
                              the Ms. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5"> <locus target="#17ra">f. 17ra</locus>
                           <desc>-b: Unclear note. </desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"> <locus target="#17ra">17ra</locus>: በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ሕያው፡
                              መሐር፡ ወመስተሣህል፡ ንዌጥን፡ ጽ…</q>
                           <note> The biggest part of the note has been effaced. The only two
                              legible lines have been encircled in a frame in black ink. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6"> <locus target="#17rb">f. 17rb</locus>
                           <desc>-vb: Note on the length of days and nights of the months. </desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#17rb">17rb-</locus>vb: ሐሳብ፡ ዘመዓልት፡ ወሌሊት፡ ዘይነውህ፡ ወየሐጽር፡
                              በወርኃ፡ መስከርም፡ (sic) ፲ወ፪፡ መዓልት፡ ወ፲፡ ወ፪፡ ሌሊት፡ ክልኤሙ፡ እሩይ፡ ለወርኃ፡ ጥቅምት፡ ፲፡
                              ወ፩፡ መዓልት፡ ፲፡ ወ፫፡ ሌሊት፡ …</q>
                           <note> The note indicates the number of the long and short days and
                              nights for each month. Further computation notes are followed. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title ባህረ፡ ሐሳብ፡ is written on the front board with
                           blue paint.&#xD; - Two tables are drawn in red ink and left unfilled on
                              <locus target="#18rv">18rv</locus>&#xD; - Omitted letters or words
                           inserted interlineally: e.g., <locus target="#8ra">8ra-</locus>b, 9ra-b,
                           11ra, 11vb, 14rb, 15r.&#xD; - Omitted numeral added at the beginning of
                           the line: <locus target="#11va">11va</locus>.&#xD; - Omitted numeral
                           added at the end of the line: <locus target="#13ra">13ra</locus>.&#xD; -
                           Erasures: e.g., <locus target="#8va">8va</locus>, 9rb, 10rb, 11vb.&#xD; -
                           Immediate corrections indicated by thin lines above and below the word:
                              <locus target="#8vb">8vb</locus>, 9vb, 10rb, 14va.&#xD; - Scribbles:
                              <locus target="#12v">12v</locus>.</item>
                     </list>
                  </additions>
